{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Prometheus data source scraping the OTLP -> Prometheus stream that carries mdk's OTel metrics.",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    }
  ],
  "__requires": [
    {"type": "grafana", "id": "grafana", "name": "Grafana", "version": "9.0.0"},
    {"type": "datasource", "id": "prometheus", "name": "Prometheus", "version": "1.0.0"}
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {"type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --"},
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "description": "mdk dead-letter view: jobs that exhausted their retry budget and landed in JobStatus.DEAD_LETTER (distinct from a one-off ERROR). Derived from mdk.jobs.completed{status=dead_letter} (golden-signals counter). A non-zero, rising dead-letter rate is a poison-job / systemic-dependency signal. Operate the backlog with `mdk jobs dead-letter list|show|retry|purge` (or the /api/v1/jobs/dead-letter* routes).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": 300,
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "title": "mdk - dead-letter: triage",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## mdk - dead-letter rate\n\n**What this shows.** Jobs reaching the terminal `DEAD_LETTER` status (retry budget exhausted), from `mdk.jobs.completed{status=dead_letter}`. Distinct from `ERROR` (failed once, not retried) — a dead-letter is *we tried N times and gave up*.\n\n**Normal range.** ~0. A steady non-zero or rising trend = a poison input, a systemic dependency outage, or a too-tight retry budget.\n\n**If you see X.**\n\n- `single agent/tenant spiking` -> poison input for that target. `mdk jobs dead-letter list -a <agent>` to inspect, `... show <id>` for the error, `... retry <id>` once the cause is fixed.\n- `broad spike across agents` -> a shared dependency (provider / DB) was down long enough to exhaust budgets. Recover in bulk with `mdk jobs dead-letter retry --all` after it recovers.\n- `slow steady accumulation` -> prune stale rows with `mdk jobs dead-letter purge --before <ISO>` after triage.\n\n**Recovery.** `retry` resets a job to a fresh `QUEUED` state (attempt_count=0) so the worker reclaims it. `purge` is tenant-scoped + irreversible (admin scope)."
      }
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
      "description": "Dead-letter throughput: rate of jobs reaching DEAD_LETTER, by tenant. Source: mdk.jobs.completed{status=dead_letter}.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2, "showPoints": "never"},
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6},
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull", "sum"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (tenant) (rate(mdk_jobs_completed_total{status=\"dead_letter\", tenant=~\"$tenant\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{tenant}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Dead-letter rate by tenant (5m)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
      "description": "Dead-letter share of all terminal jobs = dead_letter / all-completed. A rising ratio means a growing fraction of work is un-recoverable by the retry policy.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 20, "lineWidth": 2, "showPoints": "never", "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "line+area"}},
          "max": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 0.02},
              {"color": "red", "value": 0.1}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14},
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(rate(mdk_jobs_completed_total{status=\"dead_letter\", tenant=~\"$tenant\"}[15m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(mdk_jobs_completed_total{tenant=~\"$tenant\"}[15m])), 1e-9)",
          "legendFormat": "dead-letter share",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Dead-letter share of completions (orange 2%, red 10%)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
      "description": "Cumulative dead-letters over the dashboard window (sum of increase). The size of the backlog awaiting `mdk jobs dead-letter` triage.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 1},
              {"color": "red", "value": 25}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14},
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(increase(mdk_jobs_completed_total{status=\"dead_letter\", tenant=~\"$tenant\"}[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "dead-letters (window)",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Dead-letters in window (backlog to triage)",
      "type": "stat"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "style": "dark",
  "tags": ["mdk", "movate", "jobs", "dead-letter", "reliability"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Data source",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "type": "datasource"
      },
      {
        "current": {"selected": false, "text": "All", "value": ".*"},
        "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
        "definition": "label_values(mdk_jobs_completed_total, tenant)",
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": true,
        "label": "tenant",
        "multi": true,
        "name": "tenant",
        "options": [],
        "query": {"query": "label_values(mdk_jobs_completed_total, tenant)", "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"},
        "refresh": 2,
        "regex": "",
        "type": "query"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": {"from": "now-6h", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "",
  "title": "mdk - dead-letter",
  "uid": "mdk-dead-letter",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": ""
}
